<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cloud Nexus</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="pill">Cloud · AI · Growth</span>
        <h1>Pioneering innovation with smart cloud solutions for growth-ready teams.</h1>
        <p>Cloud Nexus helps ambitious organizations scale with automation, secure cloud infrastructure, and next-gen talent from Bhopal's leading tech ecosystem.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="#careers">Apply as a Fresher</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="#services">Explore Services</a>
        </div>
        <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="marquee-content">
            <span class="marquee-item">AWS</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">Azure</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">Docker</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">Kubernetes</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">React</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">Python</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">Node.js</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">Terraform</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">AI & Data</span>
            <span class="marquee-item">CI/CD</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-panel">
        <div class="pill">Book a consultation</div>
        <h2>Integrated hiring & cloud discovery</h2>
        <p>Schedule a session with our recruiting and technology advisory team to discuss automation, digital transformation, or fresher hiring programs.</p>
        <div class="panel-line">
          <div>
            <strong>Next Availability</strong>
            <p style="color: var(--text-soft); margin-top: 8px;">Thursday, 10:00 AM IST</p>
          </div>
          <div class="circle"></div>
        </div>
        <a class="button button-primary" href="#contact">Request a slot</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="services" class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="highlight">Services</p>
          <h2>Modular cloud services built for performance.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Cloud Infrastructure & Management</h3>
          <p>Design, deploy, and operate resilient cloud platforms with automated observability and cost-aware architecture.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>DevOps & Agile Pipelines</h3>
          <p>Deliver faster with CI/CD, infrastructure as code, and release automation that keeps teams aligned and shipping value.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>AI, Data Science & ML</h3>
          <p>Build intelligent systems, predictive models, and data-driven products that turn raw insight into business advantage.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Web & App Development</h3>
          <p>Create modern digital experiences with secure web apps, responsive interfaces, and cloud-connected backend services.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Cybersecurity & Data Integrity</h3>
          <p>Protect your operations with proactive security, compliance-ready design, and end-to-end data safeguards.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="highlight">About Cloud Nexus</p>
          <h2>Modern IT consulting for scalable digital transformation.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <p>Cloud Nexus is a technology consulting partner focused on autonomously scaling business operations with cloud-native systems, AI workflows, and agile delivery. Our teams blend infrastructure expertise with practical automation to accelerate growth, improve reliability, and unlock new digital opportunities.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat-card">
              <strong>4</strong>
              <span>Core tech domains</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <strong>5</strong>
              <span>Day workweek, with team energy</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="careers" class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="highlight">Careers at Cloud Nexus</p>
          <h2>Life at Cloud Nexus for freshers and interns.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Built for early talent</h3>
          <p>We recruit from LNCT, SIRT, OIST, and top local colleges. Freshers get mentorship, hands-on cloud projects, and a fast-track path into consulting and engineering.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Culture & community</h3>
          <p>Our teams enjoy turf cricket weekends, knowledge-sharing sessions, flexible growth paths, and a workplace that values curiosity, empathy, and collaboration.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section contact-grid" id="contact">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>Apply now</h3>
        <p>Submit your details and resume to join Cloud Nexus as a fresher or intern. We review applications weekly and invite motivated talent to interviews quickly.</p>
        <form id="application-form" class="form-grid">
          <div>
            <label for="name">Full Name</label>
            <input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@domain.com" required />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="role">Preferred Role</label>
            <input id="role" name="role" type="text" placeholder="Cloud Engineer, Data Analyst, DevOps" />
          </div>
          <div class="file-field">
            <label class="file-label" for="resume">Choose resume file</label>
            <input id="resume" name="resume" type="file" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx" />
            <span id="file-name">No file selected</span>
          </div>
          <button class="button button-primary" type="submit">Send Application</button>
          <div id="form-status" class="success-message"></div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>Contact</h3>
        <p><strong>Address</strong><br>Kasturi Orchard, Plot No 20, Tribhuwam Vihar, Katara Hills, Bagli Village, Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh 462043</p>
        <p><strong>Email</strong><br><a href="mailto:work@cloudnexus.in">work@cloudnexus.in</a></p>
        <p><strong>Phone</strong><br><a href="tel:+919201004208">+91 92010 04208</a></p>
        <p>Cloud Nexus blends cloud ecosystems, AI workflows, and a talent-first hiring approach for businesses that need rapid, reliable growth.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 Cloud Nexus • Trusted cloud partners for modern enterprises and emerging talent.</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
  <script src="/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>